### Create book (multipart)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/livres
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--field titre=Mon livre
--field description=Description du livre
--field statut=payant
--field prix=9.99
--file fichier_pdf=@/path/to/sample.pdf
--file couverture=@/path/to/cover.jpg

### Update book (multipart)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/admin/livres/{{BOOK_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--field titre=Mon livre modifi√©
--file couverture=@/path/to/new-cover.jpg

### Delete book
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/admin/livres/{{BOOK_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>
